FuncDef:
The enable command enables the AnyFlow function.
The undo enable command disables the AnyFlow function. The enable command enables the AnyFlow function. The undo enable command disables the AnyFlow function. By default, the AnyFlow function is disabled. This command is supported only on the CE6860-SAN, CE6866K, CE6866, CE6860-HAM, CE8850-SAN, CE8851K, CE8851-32CQ8DQ-P and CE8850-HAM.
